Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper is about voice conversion, which is related to sound processing.
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper proposes a novel mixture-of-experts (MoE) based VC system that uses a gating mechanism to specify optimal weights to feature maps, which is related to natural language processing.
- cs.LG (Learning): The paper discusses the recent advancements of deep learning technologies and proposes a deep-learning-based VC system, which is related to machine learning.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the online computation efficiency of the proposed system, which is related to control systems.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a deep-learning-based VC system and discusses the performance improvement in both objective evaluations and human listening tests, which is related to artificial intelligence.
